rules 'stache or no 'stache

1. pick mustache or no mustache
 a. if chosen, you have to drink
2. select offense 
	a. if correct, you can give away the drink.
	b. otherwise, you have to take a drink.
3. if you guess a female, then everyone else has to finish their drink.
	a. otherwise, you have to finish your drink.
4. if no one guesses a woman and a woman appears, then everyone drinks.
5. when everyone guesses correctly (stache or no stache) then everyone drinks.